#. <section class="sutta" id="sn37.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.24:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "2. Abbreviated Texts"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn37.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Pañcasīlasutta"
msgstr "24. Five Precepts"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.24:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, "
"after death, they are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm."

msgctxt "sn37.24:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn37.24:1.3"
msgid ""
"Pāṇātipātā paṭivirato ca hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato ca hoti, "
"kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato ca hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato ca hoti, "
"surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato ca hoti—"
msgstr ""
"They don’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or "
"consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "sn37.24:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā "
"paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after "
"death, they are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.24:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.24:1.6"
msgid "Dutiyapeyyālavaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: ca → anuruddho (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.24:2.1"
msgid "Dutiye ca akkodhano,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.24:2.2"
msgid "anupanāhī anissukī;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.24:2.3"
msgid "Amaccharī anaticārī,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.24:2.4"
msgid "sīlavā ca bahussuto;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.24:2.5"
msgid "Vīriyaṃ sati sīlañca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn37.24:2.6"
msgid "sukkapakkhe pakāsito."
msgstr ""
